tting the help you need to manage yours.</p>\n\n\n\n    \n</div>\n\n\n    \n    \n    <div class="ctabutton ctabutton--secondary align--text-left"><div class="cta" data-cmp-is="cta">\n  <a href="https://www.truthaboutweight.ca/en/what-is-obesity.html" target="_self">\n    \n        \n            \n            <span>Understand the science of obesity</span>\n        \n    </a>\n</div>\n\n\n    \n</div>\n\n\n\n</div>\n\n\n    \n</figure>\n\n    \n</div>\n</div>\n\n  <main id="main">\n\n\n<div class="aem-Grid aem-Grid--12 aem-Grid--default--12 ">\n    \n    <div class="responsivegrid col-wide aem-GridColumn aem-GridColumn--default--12">\n\n\n<div class="aem-Grid aem-Grid--12 aem-Grid--default--12 ">\n    \n    <div class="responsivegrid aem-GridColumn aem-GridColumn--default--12">\n\n\n<div class="aem-Grid aem-Grid--12 aem-Grid--default--12 ">\n    \n    <div class="container responsivegrid bg--grey block--grey aem-GridColumn aem-GridColumn--default--12">\n\n    \n    \n    \n    <div id="container-d673ebe374" class="cmp-container">\n        \n        <section class="section-container section-container--large section-container--dwsp-medium">\n\n    \n    \n    \n    <div id="sectioncontainer-fcc5b7d0a9" class="cmp-container">\n        \n        <div class="container responsivegrid bg--green">\n\n    \n    \n    \n    <div id="container-0efbf8dac0" class="cmp-container">\n        \n        <div class="title title--sm-b title--center-text">\n  <h2 id="title-14979cb6d3" data-cmp-is="title">\n    \n      Check your BMI with a BMI calculator\n    \n  </h2>\n\n\n\n    \n\n</div>\n<div class="text text--sm">\n<p>Body mass index (BMI) is an important measurement when it comes to understanding your weight. While it should not be used to diagnose obesity, it can be used as a screening tool to classify your weight.</p>\n\n\n\n    \n</div>\n<div class="ctabutton ctabutton--secondary align--text-center"><div class="cta" data-cmp-is="cta">\n  <a href="https://www.truthaboutweight.ca/en/managing-your-weight/whats-your-body-mass-index-bmi.html" target="_self">\n    \n        \n            \n            <span>Check your BMI</span>\n        \n    </a>\n</div>\n\n\n    \n</div>\n\n        \n    </div>\n\n</div>\n\n        \n    </div>\n\n</section>\n<section class="section-container section-container--large section-container--dwsp-medium">\n\n    \n    \n    \n    <div id="sectioncontainer-99e47219f3" class="cmp-container">\n        \n        <div class="mediatext mediatext--ratio-16-9"><article class="media-text" aria-label="media with assisting text">\n  <figure class="media"><div data-cmp-is="image" data-cmp-src="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/ca/content-pages/hero-images/science-section/How-environment-affects-our-health-banner.png" data-asset="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/ca/content-pages/hero-images/science-section/How-environment-affects-our-health-banner.png" class="cmp-image">\n  \n    \n      <picture>\n        <source srcset="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/ca/content-pages/hero-images/science-section/How-environment-affects-our-health-banner.png" media="(min-width: 770px)">\n        <source srcset="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/ca/content-pages/hero-images/science-section/How-environment-affects-our-health-banner.png" media="(max-width: 769px)">\n        <img src="https://www.truthaboutweight.ca/content/dam/truthaboutweight/ca/content-pages/hero-images/science-section/How-environment-affects-our-health-banner.png" loading="lazy" class="cmp-image__image" data-cmp-hook-image="image" alt="">\n      </picture>\n      \n    \n  \n  \n</div>\n\n    \n</figure>\n  <section class="quote-area" itemprop="description">\n\n\n\n\n    \n    \n    <div class="title title--sm-b">\n  <h2 id="title-8a4613baf5" data-cmp-is="title">\n    \n      Obesity and our modern food environment \n    \n  </h2>\n\n\n\n    \n\n</div>\n\n\n    \n    \n    <div class="text text--sm">\n<p>Our genes have not changed much in the past 50,000 years. But the world we live in and