ologie qui, toutes générations confondues, affecte 10 millions de Français, s’affronte avec méthode et motivation. Voici quelques pistes pour comprendre la maladie et prendre soin de soi.</p>\n\n\n\n    \n</div>\n\n\n    \n    \n    <div class="ctabutton ctabutton--primary align--text-left"><div class="cta" data-cmp-is="cta">\n  <a href="https://www.audeladupoids.fr/obesite-et-surpoids/jai-decide-dagir-pour-moi-et-pour-ma-sante.html" target="_self">\n    \n        \n            \n            <span>Lire la suite</span>\n        \n    </a>\n</div>\n\n\n    \n</div>\n\n\n</section>\n</article>\n\n    \n</div>\n\n        \n    </div>\n\n</section>\n<section class="section-container section-container--large section-container--dwsp-large">\n\n    \n    \n    \n    <div id="sectioncontainer-e39b190959" class="cmp-container">\n        \n        <div class="splitlayout parbase splitlayout--align-top"><div class="columns threeCol ">\n\n  \n  \n\n  \n  \n\n  \n  \n  \n    \n    <div class="column threeCol  ">\n\n\n\n\n    \n    \n    <div class="mediatext mediatext--ratio-16-9"><article class="media-text" aria-label="media with assisting text">\n  <figure class="media"><div data-cmp-is="image" data-cmp-src="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/fr/content-pages/teasers/Article-Nos-Dessins-pour-lavenir-teaser.png" data-asset="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/fr/content-pages/teasers/Article-Nos-Dessins-pour-lavenir-teaser.png" class="cmp-image">\n  \n    \n      <picture>\n        <source srcset="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/fr/content-pages/teasers/Article-Nos-Dessins-pour-lavenir-teaser.png" media="(min-width: 770px)">\n        <source srcset="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/fr/content-pages/teasers/Article-Nos-Dessins-pour-lavenir-teaser.png" media="(max-width: 769px)">\n        <img src="https://www.audeladupoids.fr/content/dam/truthaboutweight/fr/content-pages/teasers/Article-Nos-Dessins-pour-lavenir-teaser.png" loading="lazy" class="cmp-image__image" data-cmp-hook-image="image" alt="