align: left;\n"><b>Obésité en Europe : l’Organisation mondiale de la santé tire la sonnette d’alarme</b></p>\n\n\n\n    \n</div>\n\n\n    \n    \n    <div class="text text--sm">\n<p style="\ttext-align: left;\n">Dans un rapport publié début mai 2022, l’OMS estime que les taux d'obésité et de surcharge pondérale ont atteint en Europe « des proportions...<br>\n<br>\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n    \n</div>\n\n\n    \n    \n    <div class="ctabutton ctabutton--primary align--text-left"><div class="cta" data-cmp-is="cta">\n  <a href="https://www.audeladupoids.fr/obesite-et-esociete/obesite-en-europe.html" target="_self">\n    \n        \n            \n            <span>Lire la suite</span>\n        \n    </a>\n</div>\n\n\n    \n</div>\n\n\n</section>\n</article>\n\n    \n</div>\n\n\n</div>\n  \n\n\n  \n  \n\n  \n  \n</div></div>\n<div class="splitlayout parbase splitlayout--align-top"><div class="columns threeCol ">\n\n  \n  \n\n  \n  \n\n  \n  \n  \n    \n    <div class="column threeCol  ">\n\n\n\n\n    \n    \n    <div class="mediatext mediatext--ratio-16-9"><article class="media-text" aria-label="media with assisting text">\n  <figure class="media"><div data-cmp-is="image" data-cmp-src="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/fr/content-pages/teasers/v4-revamp-teasers/Article-ObesiteeteconomiemondialeFR23OB00164.png" data-asset="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/fr/content-pages/teasers/v4-revamp-teasers/Article-ObesiteeteconomiemondialeFR23OB00164.png" class="cmp-image">\n  \n    \n      \n      <picture>\n        <source media="(min-width:1040px)" srcset="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/fr/content-pages/teasers/v4-revamp-teasers/Article-ObesiteeteconomiemondialeFR23OB00164.png">\n        <source media="(min-width:700px)" srcset="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/fr/content-pages/teasers/v4-revamp-teasers/Article-ObesiteeteconomiemondialeFR23OB00164.png">\n        <img loading="lazy" class="cmp-image__image" data-cmp-hook-image="image" alt="">\n      </picture>\n    \n  \n  \n</div>\n\n    \n</figure>\n  <section class="quote-area" itemprop="description">\n\n\n\n\n    \n    \n    <div class="text text--sm">\n<p style="\ttext-align: left;\n"><b>Une étude mesure l’impact de l’obésité sur la croissance de l'économie mondiale</b></p>\n\n\n\n    \n</div>\n\n\n    \n    \n    <div class="text text--sm">\n<p style="\ttext-align: left;\n">Selon une étude de la revue BMJ Global Health, les taux d’obésité en constante augmentation coûteront à l’économie mondiale 3,29 % de son PIB d’ici 2060...<br>\n</p>\n\n\n\n    \n</div>\n\n\n    \n    \n    <div class="ctabutton ctabutton--primary align--text-left"><div class="cta" data-cmp-is="cta">\n  <a href="https://www.audeladupoids.fr/obesite-et-esociete/une-etude-mesure-limpact-de-lobesite.html" target="_self">\n    \n        \n            \n            <span>Lire la suite</span>\n        \n    </a>\n</div>\n\n\n    \n</div>\n\n\n</section>\n</article>\n\n    \n</div>\n\n\n</div>\n  \n    \n    <div class="column threeCol  ">\n\n\n\n\n</div>\n  \n    \n    <div class="column threeCol  ">\n\n\n\n\n</div>\n  \n\n\n  \n  \n\n  \n  \n</div></div>\n<div class="ctabutton ctabutton--secondary align--text-center"><div class="cta" data-cmp-is="cta">\n  <a href="https://www.audeladupoids.fr/obesite-et-esociete.html" target="_self">\n    \n        \n            \n            <span>Tous les articles</span>\n        \n    </a>\n</div>\n\n\n    \n</div>\n<div class="text">\n\n    \n</div>\n\n        \n    </div>\n\n</section>\n<section class="section-container section-container--large section-container--dwsp-medium">\n\n    \n    \n    \n    <div id="sectioncontainer-06e7a6fe32" class="cmp-container">\n        \n        \n        \n    </div>\n\n</section>\n<section class="section-container section-container--large section-container--dwsp-medium">\n\n    \n    \n    \n    <div id="sectioncontainer-cf2816f5eb" class="cmp-container">\n        \n        <div class="title title--sm">\n  <h2 id="title-1ce56b3daa" data-cmp-is="title">\n    \n