-test-image1.png" loading="lazy" class="cmp-image__image" data-cmp-hook-image="image" alt="">\n      </picture>\n      \n    \n  \n  \n</div>\n\n    \n</div>\n<div class="title title--center-text">\n  <h2 id="title-be18f62a2b" data-cmp-is="title">\n    \n      Jūsu vidukļa apkārtmērs sniedz informāciju par jūsu veselību\n    \n  </h2>\n\n\n\n    \n\n</div>\n<div class="text text--sm text--center-text">\n<p>Tauki ap vidukli&nbsp;– viscerālie tauki&nbsp;– var palielināt sirds un asinsvadu slimību risku pat ar veselīgu ĶMI. Jūsu vidukļa apkārtmēra mērīšana sniedz jums galvenos ieskatus attiecībā uz jūsu veselību.</p>\n\n\n\n    \n</div>\n<div class="ctabutton ctabutton--secondary align--text-center">\n\n\n    \n</div>\n\n        \n    </div>\n\n</section>\n<section class="section-container section-container--large section-container--dwsp-medium">\n\n    \n    \n    \n    <div id="sectioncontainer-f9ae98e218" class="cmp-container">\n        \n        <div class="mediatext mediatext--ratio-16-9"><article class="media-text" aria-label="media with assisting text">\n  <figure class="media">\n<div style="width:100%; height:0; position: relative; padding-bottom:56.2795089707271%"><div title="Video Player" src="https://nn-product.videomarketingplatform.co/108772968.thtml?token=72320ba83766971aced7b0fcfa7f4dac&amp;source=embed&amp;photo%5fid=108772968" style="width:100%; height:100%; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0;" frameborder="0" border="0" scrolling="no" allowfullscreen="" allow="autoplay; fullscreen" data-original-tag="iframe">\n    \n  \n  \n    <img src="https://nn-product.videomarketingplatform.co/64968566/108772968/72320ba83766971aced7b0fcfa7f4dac/625xcr/thumbnail.jpg" width="100%" height="100%">\n    <a href="https://nn-product.videomarketingplatform.co/108772968.ihtml?source=embed&amp;token=72320ba83766971aced7b0fcfa7f4dac&amp;photo%5fid=108772968&amp;autoPlay=1"></a>\n    \n  \n\n\n</div></div>\n\n\n    \n</figure>\n  <section class="quote-area" itemprop="description">\n\n\n\n\n</section>\n</article>\n\n    \n</div>\n\n        \n    </div>\n\n</section>\n<section class="section-container section-container--small section-container--dwsp-medium">\n\n    \n    \n    \n    <div id="sectioncontainer-cfbf345da2" class="cmp-container">\n        \n        <div class="mediatext mediatext--left"><article class="media-text" aria-label="media with assisting text">\n  <figure class="media"><div data-cmp-is="image" data-cmp-src="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/gif/hearthealth-obesity-1.gif" data-asset="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/gif/hearthealth-obesity-1.gif" data-title="sirdsveselība-aptaukošanās-1" class="cmp-image">\n  \n    \n      <picture>\n        <source srcset="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/gif/hearthealth-obesity-1.gif" media="(min-width: 770px)">\n        <source srcset="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/gif/hearthealth-obesity-1.gif" media="(max-width: 769px)">\n        <img src="https://www.manssvars.lv/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/gif/hearthealth-obesity-1.gif" loading="lazy" class="cmp-image__image" data-cmp-hook-image="image" alt="sirdsveselība-aptaukošanās-1">\n      </picture>\n      \n    \n  \n  \n</div>\n\n    \n</figure>\n  <section class="quote-area" itemprop="description">\n\n\n\n\n    \n    \n    <div class="title title--sm-b">\n  <h2 id="title-4b7f7825ec" data-cmp-is="title">\n    \n      Pārbaudiet savas zināšanas\n    \n  </h2>\n\n\n\n    \n\n</div>\n\n\n    \n    \n    <div class="text text--sm">\n<p>Vai vēlaties noskaidrot, kā aptaukošanās ir saistīta ar sirds veselību? Lai to uzzinātu, izpildiet šo testu. Pārbaudiet savas zināšanas un atklājiet jaunus faktus par šīm slimībām.</p>\n\n\n\n    \n</div>\n\n\n    \n    \n    <div class="ctabutton ctabutton--secondary align--text-left"><div class="cta" data-cmp-is="cta">\n  <a href="https://www.manssvars.lv/kas-ir-aptaukosanas/parbaudi-savas-zinasanas-par-aptaukosanos.html" target="_self">\n    \n        \n            \n            <span>Pildīt testu</span>\n        \n    </a>\n</div>\n\n\n    \n</div>\n\n\n</section>\n</article>\n\n    \n</div>\n<div class="richmedia">\n<br><br>\n\n\n    \n</div>\n<div class="mediatext mediatext--right"><article class="media-text" aria-label="media with assisting text">\n  <figure class="media"><div data-cmp-is="image" data-cmp-src="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/content-pages/infographics/desktop/home-test-new-design-image2.png" data-asset="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/content-pages/infographics/desktop/home-test-new-design-image2.png" class="cmp-image">\n  \n    \n      <picture>\n        <source srcset="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/content-pages/infographics/desktop/home-test-new-design-image2.png" media="(min-width: 770px)">\n        <source srcset="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/content-pages/infographics/desktop/home-test-new-design-image2.png" media="(max-width: 769px)">\n        <img src="https://www.manssvars.lv/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/content-pages/infographics/desktop/home-test-new-design-image2.png" loading="lazy" class="cmp-image__image" data-cmp-hook-image="image" alt="">\n      </picture>\n      \n    \n  \n  \n</div>\n\n    \n</figure>\n  <section class="quote-area" itemprop="description">\n\n\n\n\n    \n    \n    <div class="title title--sm-b">\n  <h2 id="title-cf649fe727" data-cmp-is="title">\n    \n      Runājiet atklāti\n    \n  </h2>\n\n\n\n    \n\n</div>\n\n\n    \n    \n    <div class="text text--sm">\n<p>Mēs saprotam, ka runāt par&nbsp;lieko svaru un&nbsp;aptaukošanos nav viegli. Tāpēc mēs esam izveidojuši ceļvedi, lai palīdzētu jums veidot atklātu un jēgpilnu sarunu ar&nbsp;jūsu veselības aprūpes speciālistu.</p>\n\n\n\n    \n</div>\n\n\n    \n    \n    <div class="ctabutton ctabutton--secondary align--text-left">\n\n\n    \n</div>\n\n\n</section>\n</article>\n\n    \n</div>\n\n        \n    </div>\n\n</section>\n<div class="richmedia">\n<br><br>\n\n\n    \n</div>\n<section class="section-container section-container--small section-container--dwsp-large">\n\n    \n    \n    \n    <div id="sectioncontainer-c6a493095e" class="cmp-container">\n        \n        <div class="title title--sm-b title--center-text">\n  <h2 id="title-18f36d1298" data-cmp-is="title">\n    \n      Jūs neesat slinks, aptaukošanās ir sarežģīta slimība\n    \n  </h2>\n\n\n\n    \n\n</div>\n<div class="text text--sm text--center-text">\n<p>Svara kontrole nav vienkārši ēšana mazāk un kustēšanās vairāk. Ģenētika, vide un citi faktori spēlē būtisku lomu attiecībā uz jūsu svaru un aptaukošanās attīstību. Jūs neesat viens. Uzziniet, kā citi uzņemas atbildību par savu veselību.</p>\n\n\n\n    \n</div>\n<div class="ctabutton ctabutton--secondary align--text-center">\n\n\n    \n</div>\n\n        \n    </div>\n\n</section>\n<section class="section-container section-container--medium">\n\n    \n    \n    \n    <div id="sectioncontainer-dfb39a60e3" class="cmp-container">\n        \n        <div class="splitlayout parbase"><div class="columns threeCol ">\n\n  \n  \n\n  \n  \n\n  \n  \n  \n    \n    <div class="column threeCol  ">\n\n\n\n\n    \n    \n    <div class="mediatext block--lightgrey"><article class="media-text" aria-label="media with assisting text">\n  <figure class="media"><div data-cmp-is="image" data-cmp-src="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/gif/icon-1.gif" data-asset="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/gif/icon-1.gif" data-title="verden-v1" class="cmp-image">\n  \n    \n      <picture>\n        <source srcset="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/gif/icon-1.gif" media="(min-width: 770px)">\n        <source srcset="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/gif/icon-1.gif" media="(max-width: 769px)">\n        <img src="https://www.manssvars.lv/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/gif/icon-1.gif" loading="lazy" class="cmp-image__image" data-cmp-hook-image="image" alt="verden-v1">\n      </picture>\n      \n    \n  \n  \n</div>\n\n    \n</figure>\n  <section class="quote-area" itemprop="description">\n\n\n\n\n    \n    \n    <div class="title title--sm-b">\n  <h2 id="title-da426b2548" data-cmp-is="title">\n    \n      +1 miljards\n    \n  </h2>\n\n\n\n    \n\n</div>\n\n\n    \n    \n    <div class="text text--sm text--center-text">\n<p>Cilvēku&nbsp;visā pasaulē dzīvo ar aptaukošanos, kas uzsver slimības sarežģītību un steidzamo nepieciešamību pēc visaptverošas rīcības aptaukošanās pārvaldībā.<br>\n<br>\n</p>\n\n\n\n    \n</div>\n\n\n</section>\n</article>\n\n    \n</div>\n\n\n</div>\n  \n    \n    <div class="column threeCol  ">\n\n\n\n\n    \n    \n    <div class="mediatext block--lightgrey"><article class="media-text" aria-label="media with assisting text">\n  <figure class="media"><div data-cmp-is="image" data-cmp-src="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/gif/icon-2.gif" data-asset="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/gif/icon-2.gif" class="cmp-image">\n  \n    \n      <picture>\n        <source srcset="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/gif/icon-2.gif" media="(min-width: 770px)">\n        <source srcset="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/gif/icon-2.gif" media="(max-width: 769px)">\n        <img src="https://www.manssvars.lv/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/gif/icon-2.gif" loading="lazy" class="cmp-image__image" data-cmp-hook-image="image" alt="">\n      </picture>\n      \n    \n  \n  \n</div>\n\n    \n</figure>\n  <section class="quote-area" itemprop="description">\n\n\n\n\n    \n    \n    <div class="title title--sm-b">\n  <h2 id="title-77c01d5b1f" data-cmp-is="title">\n    \n      40-70%\n    \n  </h2>\n\n\n\n    \n\n</div>\n\n\n    \n    \n    <div class="text text--sm text--center-text">\n<p>Aptaukošanās attīstības risku var saistīt ar ģenētiku, uzsverot, ka tas ir ne tikai gribasspēks, bet arī bioloģiskie faktori.&nbsp;<br>\n<br>\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n    \n</div>\n\n\n</section>\n</article>\n\n    \n</div>\n\n\n</div>\n  \n    \n    <div class="column threeCol  ">\n\n\n\n\n    \n    \n    <div class="mediatext block--lightgrey"><article class="media-text" aria-label="media with assisting text">\n  <figure class="media"><div data-cmp-is="image" data-cmp-src="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/gif/icon-3.gif" data-asset="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/gif/icon-3.gif" data-title="mand-v1" class="cmp-image">\n  \n    \n      <picture>\n        <source srcset="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/gif/icon-3.gif" media="(min-width: 770px)">\n        <source srcset="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/gif/icon-3.gif" media="(max-width: 769px)">\n        <img src="https://www.manssvars.lv/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/gif/icon-3.gif" loading="lazy" class="cmp-image__image" data-cmp-hook-image="image" alt="mand-v1">\n      </picture>\n      \n    \n  \n  \n</div>\n\n    \n</figure>\n  <section class="quote-area" itemprop="description">\n\n\n\n\n    \n    \n    <div class="title title--sm-b">\n  <h2 id="title-291d2e61a1" data-cmp-is="title">\n    \n      +200\n    \n  </h2>\n\n\n\n    \n\n</div>\n\n\n    \n    \n    <div class="text text--sm text--center-text">\n<p>Aptaukošanās ir saistīta ar vairāk nekā 200&nbsp;veselības komplikācijām.</p>\n<p><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n    \n</div>\n\n\n</section>\n</article>\n\n    \n</div>\n\n\n</div>\n  \n\n\n  \n  \n\n  \n  \n</div></div>\n<div class="ctabutton ctabutton--secondary cta-button--sticky-br cta-button--with-search-icon">\n\n\n    \n</div>\n<div class="splitlayout parbase"><div class="columns threeCol ">\n\n  \n  \n\n  \n  \n\n  \n  \n  \n    \n    <div class="column threeCol  ">\n\n\n\n\n    \n    \n    <div class="mediatext block--lightgrey mediatext--ratio-16-9"><article class="media-text" aria-label="media with assisting text">\n  <figure class="media"><div data-cmp-is="image" data-cmp-src="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/gif/icon-4.gif" data-asset="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/gif/icon-4.gif" data-title="mērlente-v1" class="cmp-image">\n  \n    \n      <picture>\n        <source srcset="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/gif/icon-4.gif" media="(min-width: 770px)">\n        <source srcset="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/gif/icon-4.gif" media="(max-width: 769px)">\n        <img src="https://www.manssvars.lv/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/gif/icon-4.gif" loading="lazy" class="cmp-image__image" data-cmp-hook-image="image" alt="mērlente-v1">\n      </picture>\n      \n    \n  \n  \n</div>\n\n    \n</figure>\n  <section class="quote-area" itemprop="description">\n\n\n\n\n    \n    \n    <div class="title title--sm-b">\n  <h2 id="title-ba092ee21b" data-cmp-is="title">\n    \n      &lt;&nbsp;0,5 attiecība\n    \n  </h2>\n\n\n\n    \n\n</div>\n\n\n    \n    \n    <div class="text text--sm">\n<p>Lai sirds būtu veselīgāka, vidukļa apkārtmēram jābūt mazākam par pusi no auguma garuma.</p>\n<p><br>\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n    \n</div>\n\n\n</section>\n</article>\n\n    \n</div>\n\n\n</div>\n  \n    \n    <div class="column threeCol  ">\n\n\n\n\n    \n    \n    <div class="mediatext block--lightgrey mediatext--ratio-16-9"><article class="media-text" aria-label="media with assisting text">\n  <figure class="media"><div data-cmp-is="image" data-cmp-src="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/gif/icon-5.gif" data-asset="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/gif/icon-5.gif" data-title="hjerte-v1" class="cmp-image">\n  \n    \n      <picture>\n        <source srcset="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/gif/icon-5.gif" media="(min-width: 770px)">\n        <source srcset="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/gif/icon-5.gif" media="(max-width: 769px)">\n        <img src="https://www.manssvars.lv/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/gif/icon-5.gif" loading="lazy" class="cmp-image__image" data-cmp-hook-image="image" alt="hjerte-v1">\n      </picture>\n      \n    \n  \n  \n</div>\n\n    \n</figure>\n  <section class="quote-area" itemprop="description">\n\n\n\n\n    \n    \n    <div class="title title--sm-b">\n  <h2 id="title-7f79070e7e" data-cmp-is="title">\n    \n      5%\n    \n  </h2>\n\n\n\n    \n\n</div>\n\n\n    \n    \n    <div class="text text--sm">\n<p>Liekā svara samazināšana&nbsp;par 5% var uzlabot sirds veselību un dzīves kvalitāti.</p>\n<p><br>\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n    \n</div>\n\n\n</section>\n</article>\n\n    \n</div>\n\n\n</div>\n  \n    \n    <div class="column threeCol  ">\n\n\n\n\n    \n    \n    <div class="mediatext block--lightgrey mediatext--ratio-16-9"><article class="media-text" aria-label="media with assisting text">\n  <figure class="media"><div data-cmp-is="image" data-cmp-src="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/gif/icon-6.gif" data-asset="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/gif/icon-6.gif" data-title="vaegt-v1" class="cmp-image">\n  \n    \n      <picture>\n        <source srcset="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/gif/icon-6.gif" media="(min-width: 770px)">\n        <source srcset="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/gif/icon-6.gif" media="(max-width: 769px)">\n        <img src="https://www.manssvars.lv/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/gif/icon-6.gif" loading="lazy" class="cmp-image__image" data-cmp-hook-image="image" alt="vaegt-v1">\n      </picture>\n      \n    \n  \n  \n</div>\n\n    \n</figure>\n  <section class="quote-area" itemprop="description">\n\n\n\n\n    \n    \n    <div class="title title--sm-b">\n  <h2 id="title-b99a552474" data-cmp-is="title">\n    \n      2,9&nbsp;x\n    \n  </h2>\n\n\n\n    \n\n</div>\n\n\n    \n    \n    <div class="text text--sm">\n<p>Cilvēkiem ar aptaukošanos ir 2,9&nbsp;reizes lielāka iespēja sasniegt savu svara samazināšanas  mērķi,&nbsp;ja tiek strādāts kopā ar veselības aprūpes speciālistu, kas specializējas aptaukošanas ārstēšanā.</p>\n\n\n\n    \n</div>\n\n\n</section>\n</article>\n\n    \n</div>\n\n\n</div>\n  \n\n\n  \n  \n\n  \n  \n</div></div>\n\n        \n    </div>\n\n</section>\n<section class="section-container section-container--small">\n\n    \n    \n    \n    <div id="sectioncontainer-e9e711c3fa" class="cmp-container">\n        \n        <div class="splitlayout parbase"><div class="columns twoCol ">\n\n  \n  \n\n  \n  \n  \n    \n    <div class="column twoCol  ">\n\n\n\n\n    \n    \n    <div class="mediatext block--lightgrey"><article class="media-text" aria-label="media with assisting text">\n  <figure class="media"><div data-cmp-is="image" data-cmp-src="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/content-pages/infographics/desktop/homepage-test-card-image2-v1.png" data-asset="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/content-pages/infographics/desktop/homepage-test-card-image2-v1.png" data-title="Atklājiet Truth About Weight" class="cmp-image">\n  \n    \n      <picture>\n        <source srcset="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/content-pages/infographics/desktop/homepage-test-card-image2-v1.png" media="(min-width: 770px)">\n        <source srcset="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/content-pages/infographics/desktop/homepage-test-card-image2-v1.png" media="(max-width: 769px)">\n        <img src="https://www.manssvars.lv/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/content-pages/infographics/desktop/homepage-test-card-image2-v1.png" loading="lazy" class="cmp-image__image" data-cmp-hook-image="image" alt="Atklājiet Truth About Weight">\n      </picture>\n      \n    \n  \n  \n</div>\n\n    \n</figure>\n  <section class="quote-area" itemprop="description">\n\n\n\n\n    \n    \n    <div class="title title--xs">\n  <h2 id="title-20cd6d81ea" data-cmp-is="title">\n    \n      Jūsu svara pārvaldība\n    \n  </h2>\n\n\n\n    \n\n</div>\n\n\n    \n    \n    <div class="text text--sm text--center-text">\n<p>Izpētiet zinātniski pierādītas aptaukošanās pārvaldības iespējas un izveidojiet plānu, lai sasniegtu savus mērķus.<br>\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n    \n</div>\n\n\n    \n    \n    <div class="ctabutton ctabutton--primary">\n\n\n    \n</div>\n\n\n</section>\n</article>\n\n    \n</div>\n\n\n</div>\n  \n    \n    <div class="column twoCol  ">\n\n\n\n\n</div>\n  \n\n\n  \n  \n\n  \n  \n\n  \n  \n</div></div>\n\n        \n    </div>\n\n</section>\n<sect