class="quote-area" itemprop="description">\n\n\n\n\n    \n    \n    <div class="title title--sm-b">\n  <h2 id="title-44f33c667e" data-cmp-is="title">\n    \n      Pasitikrinkite savo žinias\n    \n  </h2>\n\n\n\n    \n\n</div>\n\n\n    \n    \n    <div class="text text--sm">\n<p>Norite sužinoti kas sieja nutukimą ir širdies sveikatą? Atlikite šį trumpą testą ir pasitikrinkite savo žinias.</p>\n\n\n\n    \n</div>\n\n\n    \n    \n    <div class="ctabutton ctabutton--secondary align--text-left"><div class="cta" data-cmp-is="cta">\n  <a href="https://www.manosvoris.lt/kas-yra-nutukimas/core-knowledge-quiz.html" target="_self">\n    \n        \n            \n            <span>Atlikite testą</span>\n        \n    </a>\n</div>\n\n\n    \n</div>\n\n\n</section>\n</article>\n\n    \n</div>\n<div class="mediatext mediatext--ratio-16-9">\n\n    \n</div>\n<div class="richmedia">\n<br><br>\n\n\n    \n</div>\n<div class="mediatext mediatext--right"><article class="media-text" aria-label="media with assisting text">\n  <figure class="media"><div data-cmp-is="image" data-cmp-src="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/content-pages/infographics/desktop/home-test-new-design-image2.png" data-asset="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/content-pages/infographics/desktop/home-test-new-design-image2.png" class="cmp-image">\n  \n    \n      <picture>\n        <source srcset="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/content-pages/infographics/desktop/home-test-new-design-image2.png" media="(min-width: 770px)">\n        <source srcset="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/content-pages/infographics/desktop/home-test-new-design-image2.png" media="(max-width: 769px)">\n        <img src="https://www.manosvoris.lt/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/content-pages/infographics/desktop/home-test-new-design-image2.png" loading="lazy" class="cmp-image__image" data-cmp-hook-image="image" alt="">\n      </picture>\n      \n    \n  \n  \n</div>\n\n    \n</figure>\n  <section class="quote-area" itemprop="description">\n\n\n\n\n    \n    \n    <div class="title title--sm-b">\n  <h2 id="title-1602c9cf54" data-cmp-is="title">\n    \n      Pasikalbėkime atvirai\n    \n  </h2>\n\n\n\n    \n\n</div>\n\n\n    \n    \n    <div class="text text--sm">\n<p>Suprantame, kad nutukimo ir antsvorio tema nėra maloni. Štai kodėl sukūrėme žinyną, kuris padės Jums atvirai pasikalbėti su sveikatos priežiūros specialistu.</p>\n\n\n\n    \n</div>\n\n\n    \n    \n    <div class="ctabutton ctabutton--secondary align--text-left"><div class="cta" data-cmp-is="cta">\n  <a href="https://www.manosvoris.lt/managing-your-weight/pasikalbekime-13-klausimu.html" target="_self">\n    \n        \n            \n            <span>Žinynas pateiktas čia</span>\n        \n    </a>\n</div>\n\n\n    \n</div>\n\n\n</section>\n</article>\n\n    \n</div>\n\n        \n    </div>\n\n</section>\n<section class="section-container">\n\n    \n    \n    \n    <div id="sectioncontainer-386e643737" class="cmp-container">\n        \n        \n        \n    </div>\n\n</section>\n<section class="section-container section-container--small section-container--dwsp-large">\n\n    \n    \n    \n    <div id="sectioncontainer-c31d9eaa1a" class="cmp-container">\n        \n        <div class="title title--sm-b title--center-text">\n  <h2 id="title-30846e792c" data-cmp-is="title">\n    \n      Nutukimas – sudėtinga liga, kurią reikia gydyti\n    \n  </h2>\n\n\n\n    \n\n</div>\n<div class="text text--sm text--center-text">\n<p>Svorio valdymas yra daug sudėtingesnis, neivien mažiau valgyti ir daugiau judėti. Genetika, aplinka ir kiti veiksniai atlieka svarbų vaidmenį Jūsų svorio raidai. Sužinokite, kaip galite rūpintis savo sveikata.</p>\n\n\n\n    \n</div>\n<div class="ctabutton ctabutton--secondary align--text-center">\n\n\n    \n</div>\n\n        \n    </div>\n\n</section>\n<section class="section-container section-container--medium">\n\n    \n    \n    \n    <div id="sectioncontainer-c9e5fbe703" class="cmp-container">\n        \n        <div class="splitlayout parbase"><div class="columns threeCol ">\n\n  \n  \n\n  \n  \n\n  \n  \n  \n    \n    <div class="column threeCol  ">\n\n\n\n\n    \n    \n    <div class="mediatext block--lightgrey"><article class="media-text" aria-label="media with assisting text">\n  <figure class="media"><div data-cmp-is="image" data-cmp-src="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/gif/icon-1.gif" data-asset="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/gif/icon-1.gif" data-title="„verden-v1“" class="cmp-image">\n  \n    \n      <picture>\n        <source srcset="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/gif/icon-1.gif" media="(min-width: 770px)">\n        <source srcset="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/gif/icon-1.gif" media="(max-width: 769px)">\n        <img src="https://www.manosvoris.lt/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/gif/icon-1.gif" loading="lazy" class="cmp-image__image" data-cmp-hook-image="image" alt="„verden-v1“">\n      </picture>\n      \n    \n  \n  \n</div>\n\n    \n</figure>\n  <section class="quote-area" itemprop="description">\n\n\n\n\n    \n    \n    <div class="title title--sm-b">\n  <h2 id="title-0218c41215" data-cmp-is="title">\n    \n      Daugiau nei 1&nbsp;milijardas\n    \n  </h2>\n\n\n\n    \n\n</div>\n\n\n    \n    \n    <div class="text text--sm text--center-text">\n<p>Žmonių kenčia nuo nutukimo visame pasaulyje – tai rodo ligos sudėtingumą ir neatidėliotiną poreikį visapusiškai gydyti nutukimą<br>\n<br>\n</p>\n\n\n\n    \n</div>\n\n\n</section>\n</article>\n\n    \n</div>\n\n\n</div>\n  \n    \n    <div class="column threeCol  ">\n\n\n\n\n    \n    \n    <div class="mediatext block--lightgrey"><article class="media-text" aria-label="media with assisting text">\n  <figure class="media"><div data-cmp-is="image" data-cmp-src="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/gif/icon-2.gif" data-asset="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/gif/icon-2.gif" class="cmp-image">\n  \n    \n      <picture>\n        <source srcset="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/gif/icon-2.gif" media="(min-width: 770px)">\n        <source srcset="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/gif/icon-2.gif" media="(max-width: 769px)">\n        <img src="https://www.manosvoris.lt/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/gif/icon-2.gif" loading="lazy" class="cmp-image__image" data-cmp-hook-image="image" alt="">\n      </picture>\n      \n    \n  \n  \n</div>\n\n    \n</figure>\n  <section class="quote-area" itemprop="description">\n\n\n\n\n    \n    \n    <div class="title title--sm-b">\n  <h2 id="title-16b0a56184" data-cmp-is="title">\n    \n      40–70&nbsp;%\n    \n  </h2>\n\n\n\n    \n\n</div>\n\n\n    \n    \n    <div class="text text--sm text--center-text">\n<p>Nutukimo&nbsp;išsivystymo lemia genetika, o tai rodo, kad nutukimas susijęs ne tik su valia, bet ir su biologiniais veiksniais.<br>\n<br>\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n    \n</div>\n\n\n</section>\n</article>\n\n    \n</div>\n\n\n</div>\n  \n    \n    <div class="column threeCol  ">\n\n\n\n\n    \n    \n    <div class="mediatext block--lightgrey"><article class="media-text" aria-label="media with assisting text">\n  <figure class="media"><div data-cmp-is="image" data-cmp-src="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/gif/icon-3.gif" data-asset="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/gif/icon-3.gif" data-title="„mand-v1“" class="cmp-image">\n  \n    \n      <picture>\n        <source srcset="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/gif/icon-3.gif" media="(min-width: 770px)">\n        <source srcset="/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/gif/icon-3.gif" media="(max-width: 769px)">\n        <img src="https://www.manosvoris.lt/content/dam/truthaboutweight/shared/gif/icon-3.gif" loading="lazy" class="cmp-image__image" data-cmp-hook-image="image" alt="„mand-v1“">\n      </picture>\n      \n    \n  \n  \n</div>\n\n    \n</figure>\n  <section class="quote-area" itemprop="description">\n\n\n\n\n    \n    \n    <div class="title title--sm-b">\n  <h2 id="title-c545e68d87" data-cmp-is="title">\n    \n      +200\n    \n  </h2>\